data.description: One-of-a-kind opportunity to own a two-story waterfront home in desirable Lakeside Estates in Kissimmee, FL. This large 4-bedroom, 2.5 bath home features open living spaces with a spacious living room and formal dining room facing scenic nature views. Vaulted ceilings and oversized windows offer tons of natural light throughout. The kitchen is spacious and was completely renovated this year.featuring an eat-in space that serves as a perfect breakfast nook, overlooking the front yard. A screened patio faces a serene pond, for extra leisurely enjoyment. The first-floor master bedroom features a large master bathroom with dual vanities and ample closet space. Upstairs, you will find three additional bedrooms and another full bathroom. The roof and HVAC were both replaced in 2018. The owner changed 5 windows to the house for greater efficiency and added a solar panel system, resulting in energy savings of more than 100%.  The property is located under 30 minutes away from Disney and Orlando International Airport and less than 15 minutes away from Osceola Regional Medical Center. Walking distance from local schools, shopping, dining, and entertainment. This house will not last so call today to book a walkthrough.
